{"tid":1875832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"偷走僅警告 何栢良轟放任","createTime":"2020-02-12T04:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T05:22:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"88f8ba9bb7252e055a737415cf0b1a96beedc789","tid":1875832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200212/WUW3HBJ3RTXNVXMNOBG2G7D2DY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200212%2FWUW3HBJ3RTXNVXMNOBG2G7D2DY%2F&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=2427c22b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200212%2FWUW3HBJ3RTXNVXMNOBG2G7D2DY%2F&h=4ccaa76d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200212/WUW3HBJ3RTXNVXMNOBG2G7D2DY/</a><br />\n<br />\n偷走僅警告 何栢良轟放任<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200212/large/1581439004_2bef.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200212%2Flarge%2F1581439004_2bef.gif&h=617c1d7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何良認為，違反隔離令個案應馬上檢控。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府日前交代內地入境本港人士的強制檢疫情況，發現九人一度離開指定檢疫地點。港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良認為，違反隔離令個案應馬上上法庭檢控，又慨嘆本港就防疫付出很大代價，「緊急立法都唔去執法，我完全睇唔到道理何在」。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良昨接受商台訪問時，談及政府強制檢疫措施及成效。他批評措施原意強制，但實際只靠自律，結果「接受檢疫嘅人走來走去」。他指政府公佈有九名接受強制隔離人士一度離開指定檢疫地點，其中七人尋回，但僅予以警告；另外兩人正通緝。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良認為「仲只係警告了事，我個人覺得完全唔可以接受，亦都令到法律好冇尊嚴」，認為應立即檢控個違反隔離令個案，「如果你放任唔理，只會一錯再錯，向市民傳達一個好錯嘅訊息」。<br />\n<br />\n何又認為疫情嚴重，「我哋每個人都要做啲嘢」，包括注重廁所環境衞生，蓋上廁板沖廁，地下去水渠位置U形隔器每日灌入最少500毫升清水，並應經常用𤩹液和酒精搓手液清潔雙手，外出要戴外科口罩，亦應避免去人多擠迫或者不通風的地方，親戚朋友聚會亦可免則免。"},{"pid":"83faa6d176741f29ff2a80655f36cfa84df55f99","tid":1875832,"uid":66569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:31:21.000Z","msg":"支持警察，嚴正執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2470adc29e1420287eaa4e1c37a0727fbddf4e23","tid":1875832,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:38:36.000Z","msg":"放任佢的通街走，就似被一個有致命殺傷性武器的人四圍殺人⋯⋯，政府不執法，就是同謀"},{"pid":"55b9a75ea8c30b967bf3da3c70918f89f0d64fb1","tid":1875832,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0d28c4b2ff005c4cea0df64639c932a0b67a72","tid":1875832,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"呢d 撚樣又唔告，on9"}]}